<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿！<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />！<delay frames="30" />
你就别犯倔脾气了，<delay8 />
