	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="10" b="12" /><size value="150" />我不要！<size value="100" /><20_2 arg="4" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Fuming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我说不要就是不要！<delay frames="30" />
你什么意思嘛！<delay20 />
为什么我非得道歉不可呀？<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
看你这话说的！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然对方都那样说了，<delay20 />
你只要服个软，<delay8 /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />问题不就解决了么！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你这太赖皮了！<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />真是不敢相信<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
好像错完全在我一样！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Worried" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />都到这种程度了，<delay20 />
还要争个谁错谁对有什么用啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谁都不服软，<delay8 />
这事儿怎么解决啊？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还是说，<delay20 />你准备直接干一架？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃！<delay20 />
干架？<delay frames="40" />
你的意思是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要我们打起来？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对啊！<delay frames="30" />
你要是真有这决心，我也不拦你了<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，会很痛的哦～！<delay frames="40" />还会流血哦～！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />噫～！<delay frames="40" />
我讨厌流血！<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我也怕痛～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那没办法了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
只能我去道歉了吗！</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这就对了嘛！<delay frames="30" />
吵架什么的，<delay20 />
先解决矛盾的人才是赢家！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你先去道歉，<delay8 />
显得你多大度呀！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">总感觉<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你好厉害！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特别给人一种<delay8 />安全感！<anim id="OhGeez" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你这孩子还真是不让人省心啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<20_3 arg="6" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />
你也帮忙劝劝她吧！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="011_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">去道歉吧</message>
	<message label="011_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你不用道歉</message>
	<message label="011_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我还有事……</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />连<tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><20_2 arg="5" />
都跟着这么说吗？！<pageBreak /><anim id="Crying" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呜呜～！<delay20 />
根本没有人站在我这边了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你误会了，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />！<delay frames="30" />
<tag a="110" b="3" /><delay20 />也是希望你们<delay8 />
能尽快和好，想要看到你开心地笑啊！<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="6" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你说，<delay20 />是这意思吧？</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的吗<20_2 arg="5" /><tag a="110" b="0" />？<20_2 arg="5" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="75" />吸溜……<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我懂了！<delay20 />
我这就去<delay20 />道歉！<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="7" />还有许多粉丝们
想要看到我的笑脸，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也得成熟一点才行！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_3 arg="8" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没错、没错！<delay20 /><anim id="HappyDance" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />这才对嘛！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="6" /><delay20 />谢啦！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay frames="30" />
<20_2 arg="3" />这次多亏你帮忙了！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Shocked" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />咦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />可以吗？<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="13" />？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Serious" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />喂、<delay20 />喂！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" />？！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="5" />还是站在我这边的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我决定了！<delay frames="40" />
我要去<delay8 />道歉！<20_3 arg="5" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然<tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="13" />相信我<delay8 />
没有做错的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得这样<delay8 />就足够了！</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<20_3 arg="5" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没想到，<delay20 />你还挺成熟的嘛！<20_2 arg="7" /><pageBreak /><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很好！<delay20 />这么做很帅哦！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />趁你没改变主意，<delay8 />赶紧去吧<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="8" /><anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />～～～！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />我绝对，<20_2 arg="5" /><delay20 /><anim id="Fuming" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />绝～对<delay frames="40" />不会道歉的！<10_4 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的决心<delay8 />可是很坚定的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="6" /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />唉～<delay frames="30" />
这下<delay8 />麻烦了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_1 arg="N0&gt;N1, N1&gt;N0" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像你这样的女孩子，<delay20 />
比起这种地方，<delay8 />
应该更喜欢大城市吧？</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我呢～<delay20 />要把自己包装成
“生活在原·无人岛上的个性派偶像”，<delay8 />
用这个身份来出道！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个行业啊，<delay20 />
没有人设是无法立足的！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在偶像的背后，<delay8 />可是存在着生存竞争哦！</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是在这种地方，<delay20 />
你要怎么了解最新的潮流变化啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在这岛上<delay8 />连杂志都少得可怜，<delay20 />
电视节目更是<delay8 />非常有限啊。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊？！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的耶～！<delay20 />
怎么办～<delay8 />这不得了啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～<delay8 />既然这样的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只能由我来创造流行了！</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦！<delay20 />很乐观嘛～！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很喜欢你这样的个性哦！</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那好，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />就是
摄影师啦！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><20_2 arg="8" />然后呢，<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="13" />就是
<20_2 arg="6" />我的制作人！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你们两位，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="5" />可要好好传达出
我的魅力哦！<delay frames="40" />
拜托啦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这算啥情况啊？！<delay frames="30" />
<20_3 arg="6" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，你倒是也说句话啊！<delay20 /><20_3 arg="4" /></message>
	<message label="107_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不行的</message>
	<message label="107_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我会努力的</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" />
也说不行的啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你们两个都没必要那么谦虚啦～！<20_2 arg="6" /><anim id="Sighing" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好～！<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="33" />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />偶像计划，<delay20 />启动～～～！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你没开玩笑吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="4" />算了，<delay8 />估计很快就会玩腻了吧……<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我～<delay8 />是～<delay8 />说～！<delay frames="40" />
你现在就开始担心自己的歌大卖之后的事，<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />未免也太早了吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你难道不应该<delay8 />先考虑一下
怎么出歌这件事吗！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />“<tag a="110" b="5" />”？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
你刚才说了“<tag a="110" b="5" />”吗？</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊？<delay20 />呃，<delay8 />嗯！<delay20 />
确实说了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么了吗？</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～这个真的<delay8 />太厉害了吧？！<delay20 />
超级帅气的呀！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想从今天开始用！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不是已经在说了吗<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这种事情我不会介意的，<delay8 />
你想怎么用就怎么用吧。</message>
	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的吗？！<delay20 />好耶～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />可是<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果我开始这么说了，<delay8 />
我的粉丝们就会传开来，<delay20 />
过段时候<delay8 />就会在全世界掀起热潮<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到时人家<delay8 />可能就会觉得
“<tag a="110" b="5" />”是我先开始说的了！<delay frames="30" />
这怎么办呀～！</message>
	<message label="207" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我说了！<delay20 />
现在还不是你担心这些事情的时候<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />唉～<delay20 />算了，懒得说了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
